OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FITV News reporter Sam Taylor joined
OL,7,FAndy along with his friends and family
OL,8,Fas they crossed England's tallest
OL,9,Faqueduct.
OL,11,FA dad-of-two with one of the most
OL,12,Fdangerous forms of cancer is taking on
OL,13,Fa 200-mile walking challenge to raise
OL,14,Fmoney for The Christie NHS Foundation
OL,15,FTrust.
OL,17,FAndy Bradley, from Knutsford,
OL,18,FCheshire, was given just 12 months to
OL,19,Flive after being diagnosed with a
OL,20,Fglioblastoma, the most aggressive form
OL,21,Fof brain cancer, in January 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FHe said: "For someone to tell you
OL,7,Fyou're not going to be there to look
OL,8,Fafter your boys and your wife - that
OL,9,FChristmas would be your last... It's
OL,10,Fterrifying."
OL,12,FBut 16 months on, the 60-year-old is
OL,13,Fstill able to take on the five hour
OL,14,Ftreks with his friends and family,
OL,15,Fthanks to a risky surgery and a new
OL,16,Fmedical trial.
OL,18,FAndy is one of the first patients to
OL,19,Fjoin the PORTRAIT clinical trial at
OL,20,FThe Christie, which is testing Tumour
OL,21,FTreating Fields (TT Fields) therapy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FThis treatment uses electrical fields
OL,7,Fdelivered through scalp patches and is
OL,8,Fhoped to slow tumour growth.
OL,10,FHe said: "Four pads are connected to
OL,11,Fwhat I call it the umbilical chord, a
OL,12,Fdevice that's sending signals to the
OL,13,Farea where the tumour was excavated
OL,14,Fduring surgery."
OL,16,FThe technology is relatively new and
OL,17,Fnot normally available on the NHS, and
OL,18,Fthe trial is testing for the first
OL,19,Ftime if it is effective before surgery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FAndy says the trial is "literally
OL,7,Fsaving my life" as he has seen no
OL,8,Ftumour growth since his surgery.
OL,10,FIf the findings are positive, it could
OL,11,Fbe used on a wider basis for patients
OL,12,Fin similar situations to Andy.
OL,14,FTo raise money for The Christie, Andy
OL,15,Fis walking the Greater Manchester
OL,16,FRingway - a 200 mile route around the
OL,17,FCity Region which will take him
OL,18,Fthrough every borough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,F"I wanted to do everything in my power
OL,7,Fto give them all the support and all
OL,8,Fthe resources they need to assist me
OL,9,Fand others," he said.
OL,11,FHe is just under halfway through the
OL,12,Fwalk which is split into 20 stages,
OL,13,Fbut has already hit his fundraising
OL,14,Ftarget of #10,000.
OL,16,FAndy is not taking on the challenge
OL,17,Falone. During each walk he has been
OL,18,Fjoined by friends and family, along
OL,19,Fwith his beagle Jess.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FJoining him on the Marple stretch, in
OL,7,FStockport, his son George said: "It's
OL,8,Fgiven him a new view on everything
OL,9,Fthat's happened.
OL,11,F"He's seen a way to make good of it...
OL,12,Fand that's just kind of the person
OL,13,Fthat he is.
OL,15,F"He's the type of person where no
OL,16,Fmatter what comes his way he just
OL,17,Ftakes it in his stride."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FAndy's wife Lisa added: "It's not a
OL,7,Fsurprise he's decided to do this
OL,8,Fchallenge... it's given him a lot of
OL,9,Fpurpose in the last few weeks.
OL,11,F"I think after all the treatment last
OL,12,Fyear, I knew once he got back to
OL,13,Ffeeling like himself he'd want to do
OL,14,Fsomething because he's a very selfless
OL,15,Fperson."
OL,17,FWhile Andy might have already hit his
OL,18,Ftarget, he says he will not stop
OL,19,Fwalking until he completes the entire
OL,20,F200 mile trek to say thank you to
OL,21,Fstaff at The Christie.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776946268
OL,3,CDad-of-two with brain cancer takes on
OL,4,C200 mile charity walk
OL,6,FHe said: "I live everyday like it's
OL,7,FChristmas... and I don't think there
OL,8,Fare many people on the planet who are
OL,9,Fblessed with that."
OL,11,FLisa added: "This time last year I
OL,12,Fdidn't think we'd be here. I thought
OL,13,Fwe might not have Andrew, so this is
OL,14,Famazing.
OL,16,F"For all this is devastating, it does
OL,17,Fmake you live in the moment more than
OL,18,Fyou probably would do before."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
